title: White Trash
description:
'White Trash'

Heavy Metal, 1993, 120 pages

Written by Gordon Rennie

Illustrated by Martin Emond

Weird ass book. I read it about 15 years ago, but I don't remember much about it, specifically, other than the two main characters are exaggerated caricatures of Axl Rose and an older, ass kicking Elvis, and they're on some kind of a fucked up road trip in their pink Cadillac.
